"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-06-scores-crossed-diving-olympics-2-21371660\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Andrea Spendolini-Sirieix is going for glory in the Women's 10m platform diving final this afternoon.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 101, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 25, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrea Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Spendolini-Sirieix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Diving is one of the most-loved sports at theOlympics- but those tuning in to watch are sometimes confused by the various aspects of the adrenaline-filled sport.\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chief amongst them is why some diving scores are crossed out on the TV graphics.\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  Here is everything you need to know.\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eleven judges score competitors in the synchronised diving events.\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 525, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Six of them are tasked with judging the divers' execution (three per dive), while five judge synchronisation.\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The five synchronisation judges award their marks on approach, take off, timing of movements, angles of entry, distance from the board and timings of entry.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The middle scores for each diver's execution is kept.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The highest and lowest scores are discarded, however, and this is to ensure that no single judge can have an overly significant effect on the final result.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 1006, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These scores are then multiplied by 0.6 to make them comparable to the scores which are used in individual diving competitions.\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are then multiplied by the level of difficulty which produces the final overall score.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In individual diving, the two highest and the two lowest judges' scores are discarded.\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1316, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Therefore, only the scores from the middle three scoring judges are taken into account.\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympic champion's 'genuinely inspiring' Netflix documentary watched 8,200,000 times  ArrowMORE:Olympic showjumper in tears as he explains why his horse crashed during final  ArrowMORE:Team USA perform incredible underwater dance routine to iconic 80s pop anthem  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 0.9999999997364739, \"rank\": 2.5948389275917925e-10, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 2097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1987, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res